Description: Document Viewer is a tool for reading document files, supporting PDF, DJVU, etc.
  Document Viewer is a small, fast and full-featured tool for viewing documents,
  supporting PDF and DJVU formats, multi-window and multi-tab management,
  thumbnail viewing, adding bookmarks and notes, magnifying, slide show,
  searching texts, rotation, etc.
